title: Top 5 Offenses in 2022
description:
Sheil and Ben discuss which teams will have the best offenses this season, and which teams just missed out on their top 5 lists.

Hosts: Sheil Kapadia and Ben Solak
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal and Conor Nevins
